for the elf file format: 

Some regex and other inspiration originally from: 
https://github.com/emacs-mirror/emacs/blob/master/lisp/progmodes/asm-mode.el

Also 
https://www.emacswiki.org/emacs/DerivedMode
https://www.emacswiki.org/emacs/ModeTutorial
https://www.emacswiki.org/emacs/RegularExpression

for work on hexl: 
http://opensource.apple.com//source/emacs/emacs-39/emacs/lisp/hexl.el


How to run: 

M-x load-file elf.el
M-x load-file my-hexl.el

I have an odd thing with dependencies and loading where if I don't call hexl-mode at least once before loading my-hexl it doesn't find my-hexl